{{Portal|Anglicanism}} 

'''Larry Robertson''' is the current [[Anglican Diocese of Yukon|Bishop of Yukon]].<ref>[http://anglican.yukon.net/bishops.htm Bishops of Yukon]</ref> He had previously served in the [[Anglican Diocese of The Arctic|Diocese of The Arctic]] for 34 years.<ref>[http://www.arcticnet.org/~larry/ Acticnet]</ref>

